            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-zinc-700 mb-2 flex justify-between items-center">
              PlayBeat
              <a
                href="https://github.com/UNIZAR-30226-2024-03"
                target="_blank"
                class="text-orange-500 hover:underline text-sm"
                >GitHub →</a
              >
            </h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-zinc-700 mb-3">
              <li>
                Streaming platform for music and podcasts with synchronized playback across devices.
              </li>
              <li>
