              </li>
              <li>
                Managed synchronization logic and data flow between mobile and web clients.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Tools:</strong> Astro, Vercel, Node.js, Express, PostgreSQL, React Native, Azure.
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a
              href="https://are-dev.es/posts/playbeat/"
              target="_blank"
              class="inline-block text-orange-500 hover:underline text-sm font-medium"
            >
              Read More
            </a>
          </div>


