            </h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-zinc-700">
              <li>
                Personal technical blog and YouTube channel on software engineering and modern web frameworks.
              </li>
              <li>
                Publishes tutorials, project walkthroughs, and technical insights.
              </li>
              <li><strong>Tools:</strong> Astro, Vercel, Markdown.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Energy Price Prediction -->
          <div class="p-6 border border-zinc-200 rounded-2xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all" itemtype="https://schema.org/Project">
